text: Diadelia albosquamulosa is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Breuning in 1949.BioLib.cz - Diadelia albosquamulosa. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Taxa named by Stephan von Breuning Category:Diadelia Category:Beetles described in 1949
